data.description: Carpet allowance and closing cost assistance provided with acceptable offer. Additional closing cost available with use of preferred lender for confirming loan types.  Spacious 2 Story Located in Sterling Oaks! 2543sqft. Home Features - An Open Layout * 4 Bedrooms * 2.5 Baths * 2 Living Areas * 3 Sides Brick Masonry * Tile Throughout on 1st Floor * White Cabinets with Stainless Steel Appliances and Gas Range at Kitchen * Gas Brick Fireplace at Living * Large Primary Bedroom * Separate Tub & Mudset Shower with Dual Vanity Sinks & His/Her Closets at the Primary Bath * Upgraded Lighting and Plumbing Fixtures * Fully Remodeled Secondary Bath * Covered Rear Patio Deck * Huge Exterior Storage Shed * Garage Door Opener * 2" Faux Blinds * Water Softener and more! Utility Easement behind home creates an added buffer between houses and additional privacy. Students will attend award winning NISD Schools! Conveniently located near La Cantera Mall, Seaworld, Six Flags, and Lackland AFB.
